{
  "stem": "13219.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and then what happened is, in the middle of the day, we started to run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said to Julius, I said, let's get out of here because he's going to kill us, or the Germans are going to kill us, or the Ukrainians are going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to the-- to the water, to the Sluch, and it's a good thing it wasn't too wide at that place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we swam over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was shooting with his rifle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At us, and he didn't hit us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we came out on the other side of the Sluch, of the river, there was the woods already, and we started to walk in the woods.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at night, while we walked, we met up with another six of Jewish people, which they ran away from that pogrom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there, at that time, for the fourth day we were about, I would say, 15 Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three sisters, which one of them is married to my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three sisters, two men, and a couple of married couples.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we started to walk, because we hear there is partisans in the woods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and we were-- we started waking for a few days, sleeping in the grass, and finding whatever we can.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stole potatoes in the-- in the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at night, we used to make a big hole and make a small little fire to-- to cook the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The water was a creek water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day I was drinking the water, and I saw little bugs in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But if you want to drink, you drink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we lived in the woods, and then we met some more people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the time-- after a couple of weeks, we were about 30 Jews together.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
